   Remember that n is lst's length
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      Remember that x is item i in lst
      When x is at least 2, then:
         Remember that prime is 1
         Remember that d is 2
         Do this diff of x and 2 times:
            When product of d and d is more than x, then:
               Leave the loop
            End when
            When remainder of x and d is 0, then:
               Remember that prime is 0
            End when
            Increase d
         End do
         When prime is 1, then:
            Remember that s is tostring of x
            Remember that sumdigits is 0
            Remember that j is 0
            Do this s's length times:
               Remember that c is item j in s
               Remember that digit is diff of c and 48
               Remember that sumdigits is sum of sumdigits and digit
               Increase j
            End do
            When x is more than best, then:
               Remember that best is x
